highlights.text: “女神戀愛惱(節目《女神配對計劃》主題曲)” by 戴祖儀 is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs Hong Kong, up 31 spots at #41.
Sabrina Carpenter has the most spots on Viral Songs Hong Kong. “Tears” is the highest at #13.
“用背脊唱情歌” by Gareth.T has been on Viral Songs Hong Kong the longest, at 86 days straight.
“かくれんぼ (Hide and Seek)” by PLAVE is the highest new entry on Viral Songs Hong Kong at #65.
